</description>
<parameter name="zoomEnum">
<type class="com.tridium.videoDriver.enums.BVideoZoomEnum"/>
<description>
defines which direction to zoom (in/out) if at all,&#xa; and how fast (slow,medium,fast).
</description>
</parameter>
<return>
